title: calling `/model glm-5` in telegram should work the same as `/model set glm-5`. So the set is optional and assumed default if we don't have set|fav|unfav|list|usage etc
---

calling `/model glm-5` in telegram should work the same as `/model set glm-5`. So the set is optional and assumed default if we don't have set|fav|unfav|list|usage etc
